#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Shackles"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Mallikāsutta"
msgstr "8. With Queen Mallikā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.75"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rājā pasenadi kosalo mallikāya deviyā saddhiṃ "
"uparipāsādavaragato hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time King Pasenadi of Kosala was upstairs in the stilt longhouse "
"together with Queen Mallikā."

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo mallikaṃ deviṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then the king said to the queen:"

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.4"
msgid "“atthi nu kho te, mallike, kocañño attanā piyataro”ti?"
msgstr "“Mallikā, is there anyone more dear to you than yourself?”"

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.5"
msgid "“Natthi kho me, mahārāja, kocañño attanā piyataro."
msgstr "“No, great king, there isn’t."

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.6"
msgid "Tuyhaṃ pana, mahārāja, atthañño koci attanā piyataro”ti?"
msgstr "But is there anyone more dear to you than yourself?”"

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.7"
msgid "“Mayhampi kho, mallike, natthañño koci attanā piyataro”ti."
msgstr "“For me also, Mallikā, there’s no-one.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.8:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo pāsādā orohitvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno "
"kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then King Pasenadi of Kosala came downstairs from the stilt longhouse, went "
"to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened."

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mallikāya deviyā saddhiṃ uparipāsādavaragato mallikaṃ "
"deviṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.3"
msgid "‘atthi nu kho te, mallike, kocañño attanā piyataro’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhante, mallikā devī maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.5"
msgid "‘natthi kho me, mahārāja, kocañño attanā piyataro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.6"
msgid "Tuyhaṃ pana, mahārāja, atthañño koci attanā piyataro’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.7"
msgid "Evaṃ vuttāhaṃ, bhante, mallikaṃ deviṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.8"
msgid "‘mayhampi kho, mallike, natthañño koci attanā piyataro’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.8:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etamatthaṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, knowing the meaning of this, on that occasion the Buddha recited this "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.172"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.1"
msgid "“Sabbā disā anuparigamma cetasā,"
msgstr "“Having explored every quarter with the mind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.2"
msgid "Nevajjhagā piyataramattanā kvaci;"
msgstr "one finds no-one dearer than oneself."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ piyo puthu attā paresaṃ,"
msgstr "Likewise for others, each holds themselves dear."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā na hiṃse paramattakāmo”ti."
msgstr "So one who loves themselves would not harm others.”"
